vpn-windows-if-youre = If you’re a heavy user of online video or music streaming, you can potentially avoid having your bandwidth restricted or throttled by your internet service provider by using a VPN.
vpn-windows-you-can-exclude = You can exclude certain apps with the split tunneling feature. This lets you have some apps running through the VPN while leaving others outside of the tunnel.
vpn-windows-using-a-windows = Using a Windows device on a public, unsecured Wi-Fi network makes your internet traffic information more vulnerable to network spies, and a VPN can help you keep your data private by adding a strong layer of protection.
